title: Pilot
description: An alien hiding in a small Colorado town meets the locals when they ask him to help solve a murder.

title: Homesick
description: In his first week at the clinic, Harry struggles to diagnose a strange feeling: human emotion.

title: Secrets
description: Harry races to keep his secret safe as Asta is forced to face her own past.

title: Birds of a Feather
description: Harry travels to the Ute Reservation to help Asta's grandmother and learns what it means to belong.

title: Love Language
description: A surprise visitor introduces Harry to a stressful human institution: marriage.

title: Sexy Beast
description: Harry copes with jealousy when the mayor hires an annoyingly perfect new town doctor.

title: The Green Glow
description: Fearing he's facing failure, Harry enlists an unlikely ally to help find his ship.

title: End of the World as We Know It
description: Harry must rely on Asta and D'Arcy for survival.

title: Welcome Aliens
description: Harry and Asta attend an alien convention.

title: Heroes of Patience
description: On the verge of completing his mission, Harry faces his own humanity.

title: Old Friends
description: Harry, the alien, is back on earth but doesn't remember who he is and only Asta can keep him safe.

title: The Wire
description: Harry has a plan to save Asta and himself but first he must attend the Sheriff's poker game.

title: Girls' Night
description: Harry meets a woman unlike any other and realizes that she is the key to his new mission.

title: Radio Harry
description: Is Harry building another bomb? Asta is going to find out as they go camping on the reservation.

title: Family Day
description: Harry and Asta's trip is interrupted by an uninvited relative as the town celebrates family.

title: An Alien in New York
description: Harry and Asta travel to New York looking for one of his people, but things go horribly wrong.

title: Escape from New York
description: Harry and Asta find what they are looking for but not what they need as danger closes in.

title: Alien Dinner Party
description: It's a surprise party as everyone gathers to celebrate Harry, but some dangerous guests cause havoc.

title: Autopsy
description: Asta is overwhelmed with guilt after she, Harry, and D'arcy get rid of the dead body.

title: The Ghost of Bobby Smallwood
description: Asta helps Harry learn how to deal with his newfound fear of death.

title: The Weight
description: Asta tells Dan about the shooting while Harry learns what it takes to be a good friend.

title: The Alien Within
description: Ben struggles to get the townspeople to accept the resort, while Harry and Asta find out the origins of Goliath.

title: Harry, a Parent
description: After losing the Alien Baby, Harry learns which alien race is on Earth. It's not what he expected.

title: Cat and Mouse
description: Harry goes head-to-head with one of his biggest enemies.

title: Best of Enemies
description: Harry has an unexpected partner as he tries to infiltrate a military base to find his alien baby.

title: I Believe in Aliens
description: Harry comes face to face with his greatest enemy and makes a choice that may affect Earth forever.
